OL,3,CITV News witnesses illegal work raids
OL,4,Cas charities accuse of 'scapegoating'
OL,6,FWe're embedded with an Immigration
OL,7,FEnforcement team in Bristol. They tell
OL,8,Fus they have intelligence that people
OL,9,Fare working illegally at several
OL,10,Flocations across the city.
OL,12,FAfter the officers are briefed, we
OL,13,Fhead in a van to the first stop: a
OL,14,Fnail salon.
OL,16,FA team of seven officers heads in.
OL,17,FThey make three arrests, all of them
OL,18,FVietnamese nationals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
