OL,6,FBut officers tell me this is the
OL,7,Ffourth time this nail salon has been
OL,8,Fraided in less than a year. So is this
OL,9,Fenforcement even working, or worth it,
OL,10,For just a futile game of cat and mouse?
OL,12,FI asked this question to Eddy
OL,13,FMontgomery, the Home Office Director
OL,14,Ffor Enforcement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
