OL,6,FAlready this year, more than 25,000
OL,7,Fpeople have come to the UK across the
OL,8,FChannel in so-called small boats
OL,9,Fcrossings. That's the highest number
OL,10,Frecorded for this point in a year ever.
OL,12,FIn figures shared exclusively with ITV
OL,13,FNews, the Home Office said between
OL,14,FJuly 20 and 27, a total of 1,780
OL,15,Findividuals were stopped and spoken to
OL,16,Fleading to 280 arrests for illegal
OL,17,Fworking activity.
OL,19,FI asked Eddy Montgomery whether those
OL,20,Fnumbers mean enforcement like this has
OL,21,Flittle impact on the big picture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
