OL,6,FThis enforcement comes off the back of
OL,7,Fthe Home Office announcing they will
OL,8,Fshare the addresses of hotels housing
OL,9,Fasylum seekers with the food delivery
OL,10,Fcompanies Uber Eats, Deliveroo and
OL,11,FJust Eat, to help them clamp down on
OL,12,Fasylum seekers illegally working for
OL,13,Fthose companies.
OL,15,FBut charities we spoke to say this is
OL,16,Fjust another way of "scapegoating"
OL,17,Fasylum seekers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
