OL,6,FDr Rhetta Moran, the founder of the
OL,7,Fcharity Rapar, which helps asylum
OL,8,Fseekers told us: "(Asylum seekers) are
OL,9,Fabsolutely being scapegoated and it is
OL,10,Fan extremely dangerous move by the
OL,11,Fgovernment that they really must step
OL,12,Fback from immediately.
OL,14,F"Already, in minds, an additional
OL,15,Fproblem now is (people think) people
OL,16,Fseeking asylum are now 'working
OL,17,Fillegally'.
OL,19,F"It's just more scapegoating, it takes
OL,20,Fpeople further down into a racist
OL,21,Frabbit hole."
