OL,6,FThey told us that they want to work
OL,7,Fand contribute to the UK and the
OL,8,Feconomy, rather than taking money off
OL,9,Fthe state. They described the ban on
OL,10,Fasylum seekers working as
OL,11,F"frustrating" and "degrading".
OL,13,FAfter violent attacks on hotels
OL,14,Fhousing asylum seekers in the riots of
OL,15,Fsummer 2024 - including one hotel
OL,16,Fbeing set on fire - Dr Rhetta Moran
OL,17,Fbelieves now is a time to show support
OL,18,Fto migrants.
