OL,6,FI asked Eddy Montgomery what his
OL,7,Fresponse is to asylum seekers saying
OL,8,Fthey want to work and contribute to
OL,9,Fthe UK economy while they are await
OL,10,Fdecisions on their asylum claims.
OL,12,FHe said: "We want a fair asylum
OL,13,Fsystem, but where people work
OL,14,Fillegally and don't have the right to
OL,15,Fwork, we will take robust action."
OL,17,FThe Home Office also announced on
OL,18,FFriday, August 8 that Immigration
OL,19,FEnforcement teams will receive a #5
OL,20,Fmillion funding boost to clamp down on
OL,21,Fillegal working.
