OL,6,FBut with record numbers of small boat
OL,7,Farrivals, the Conservatives say "the
OL,8,Ffacts speak for themselves". The
OL,9,FShadow Home Secretary Chris Philp said
OL,10,Fa Conservative government would
OL,11,F"deport all illegal arrivals".
OL,13,FAfter arresting the manager of the
OL,14,Fnail salon in Bristol, officers put
OL,15,Fhim in the back of the Immigration
OL,16,FEnforcement van.
OL,18,FWe then moved onto two more locations
OL,19,Fin the city, restaurants, where after
OL,20,Fenquiries, no arrests were made.
